1.title: What is Healthy with Sophie Jaffe & Sierra Nielsen
1.plot:
Know what this is about?
 Be the first one to add a plot.

imdb.plot outline: "What is 'Healthy'?" is a series focused on revealing the root, raw stories of the most popular influencers on social media, through exploring the core question that almost everyone on a health journey asks. Through uncovering their authenticity and the amazing journey these figures have had, we'll inspire you for your own health journey - getting back to your "why", your purpose, the thing that drives you to live out your vision of being healthy. Come join us for an intimate conversation, mocktails from Health-Ade, and lots of goodies.
